      <title>加拿大帝国商业银行称加拿大央行必须终止或纠正量化紧缩政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/cibc-says-bank-of-canada-must-end-or-fix-quantitative-tightening</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大帝国商业银行策略师表示，加拿大央行需要结束其量化紧缩计划，或修复导致有效利率维持在较高水平的短期融资市场扭曲现象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/cibc-says-bank-of-canada-must-end-or-fix-quantitative-tightening</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 16:55:06 GMT</pubDate>
